### **3\. How AI Makes Cloud Systems Smarter**

AI brings automation and intelligence to every part of cloud operations.

**a. Automatic Resource Management**  
 Instead of manually setting how much power or storage your system needs, AI does it for you. It checks usage in real time and adjusts to keep things running smoothly.

**b. Predicting and Preventing Problems**  
 AI studies patterns to see if something might go wrong soon. If it finds a risk, it fixes it before users even notice.

**c. Better Security**  
 AI can detect unusual activity like hacking attempts or strange logins and respond instantly to protect data.

**d. Cost Control**  
 AI makes sure you only pay for what you actually use — helping save money while keeping performance high.

These intelligent features are what make AI-powered cloud infrastructure the future of digital operations.
